\sum_{0\le n<\infty}a\cdot r^n=\frac a{1-r}=3\ \ \  \  (1)
\sum_{0\le n<\infty}a^3\cdot (r^3)^n=\frac {a^3}{1-r^3}=\frac{108}{13}\ \ \  \ (2) 
