\sum_{0\le n<\infty}a^2\cdot (r^2)^n=\frac{a^2}{1-r^2}
a_n=ar^{n-1}
a_n^2=a^2(r^2)^{n-1}
a_n^3=a^3(r^3)^{n-1}
\tag{1} \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} ar^{n-1}=3\qquad\text{and}\qquad\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}a^3(r^3)^{n-1}=\frac{108}{13}. 
